nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: The camera delves into the forest floor, revealing an intricate network of mycelium glowing faintly under UV light. A time-lapse shows mushrooms sprouting overnight, their caps unfurling like umbrellas. The camera focuses on a colorful variety: bright red fly agarics, delicate oyster mushrooms, and luminous bioluminescent fungi glowing in the dark. An overhead drone shot captures the forest canopy, while a voiceover explains how fungi connect trees in a vast underground communication network. The scene ends with a close-up of spores releasing into the air, a quiet reminder of the unseen processes that sustain life on Earth.

Enable the crop image, for fast tweaking of only a 1024x1024 section which is equivalent to one tile in the Ultimate SD upscale node. Disable it once you are happy with the results, to upscale the entire image.
